===Verb===
{{en-verb|intrigu|ing}}

# {{intransitive}} To conceive or carry out a secret plan intended to harm; to form a plot or scheme.
# {{transitive}} To arouse the [[interest]] of; to [[fascinate]].
# {{intransitive}} To have [[clandestine]] or [[illicit]] [[intercourse]].

